Privacy Policy
General Provisions
This Privacy Policy describes how the "Time Tasker" app collects, uses, and protects user information. We respect your right to privacy and are committed to safeguarding your data.

1. Information Collected
We do not collect or process personal data such as usernames, email addresses, phone numbers, or any other information that could identify an individual. All information is stored solely on your device and is used only to ensure the proper functioning of the app.

2. Local Data
To ensure the app operates correctly, we store task data, time records, and other functional information locally on your device. This data is not transmitted to our servers or any third-party servers and is used exclusively within the app.

3. Permissions
The app may request permissions to access the following resources on your device:

Access to files: To save task-related data.
Access to time and timer data: For the proper operation of the stopwatch feature.
4. Data Security
We take necessary measures to protect the data stored on your device. We recommend setting up a password or other security measures to safeguard your device.

5. Changes to the Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in the appâ€™s functionality. Any changes will be communicated on this page.

